

WORKING JPA project
persistence.xml is used for database connections
DML = data manipulation language
the queries are written in daoImpl
direct execution of queries using em and emf
em and emf are created using JpaUtility using persistence.xml

named queries are written in Entity class using @namedQueries
jpQl queries using em.createQuery("query")


some named queries are written in orm.xml

JPQL.Functions -> contains query for string and date functions
String = normal, upper, lower, substring, length
Date = normal date, year, month ,day
Math = Avg,count,sum,min,max